ou trèfle <colour id="7" />♣<colour id="65535" /> ?</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Cœur <colour id="6" />♥<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Carreau <colour id="6" />♦<colour id="65535" /></message>
